{"id":566,"parent_id":497,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":566,"title":"Psalm 69","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ps.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Psalm 69"],[".studySummary",["i","A messianic psalm of David—The zeal of the Lord’s house has eaten Him up—Reproach has broken His heart—He is given gall and vinegar to drink—He is persecuted—He will save Zion."]],[".intro","To the chief Musician upon Shoshannim,",["i","A Psalm"],"of David."]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.1","order":"02.20.069.37624"},["b","1"],"Save me, O God; for the waters are come in unto",["i","my"],"soul."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.2","order":"02.20.069.37625"},["b","2"],"I sink in deep mire, where",["i","there is"],"no standing: I am come into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"deep"],"waters, where the floods overflow me."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.3","order":"02.20.069.37626"},["b","3"],"I am weary of my crying: my throat is dried: mine eyes fail while I wait for my God."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.4","order":"02.20.069.37627"},["b","4"],"They that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"hate"],"me without a cause are more than the hairs of mine head: they that would destroy me,",["i","being"],"mine enemies wrongfully, are mighty: then I restored",["i","that"],"which I took not away."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.5","order":"02.20.069.37628"},["b","5"],"O God, thou knowest my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"foolishness"],"; and my sins are not hid from thee."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.6","order":"02.20.069.37629"},["b","6"],"Let not them that wait on thee, O Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts, be ashamed for my sake: let not those that seek thee be confounded for my sake, O God of Israel."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.7","order":"02.20.069.37630"},["b","7"],"Because for thy sake I have borne reproach; shame hath covered my face."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.8","order":"02.20.069.37631"},["b","8"],"I am become a stranger unto my brethren, and an alien unto my mother’s children."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.9","order":"02.20.069.37632"},["b","9"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"zeal"],"of thine house hath eaten me up; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"reproaches"],"of them that reproached thee are fallen upon me."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.10","order":"02.20.069.37633"},["b","10"],"When I wept,",["i","and chastened"],"my soul with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fasting"],", that was to my reproach."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.11","order":"02.20.069.37634"},["b","11"],"I made sackcloth also my garment; and I became a proverb to them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.12","order":"02.20.069.37635"},["b","12"],"They that sit in the gate speak against me; and I",["i","was"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"song"],"of the drunkards."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.13","order":"02.20.069.37636"},["b","13"],"But as for me, my prayer",["i","is"],"unto thee, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","in"],"an acceptable time: O God, in the multitude of thy mercy hear me, in the truth of thy salvation."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.14","order":"02.20.069.37637"},["b","14"],"Deliver me out of the mire, and let me not sink: let me be delivered from them that hate me, and out of the deep waters."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.15","order":"02.20.069.37638"},["b","15"],"Let not the waterflood overflow me, neither let the deep swallow me up, and let not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"pit"],"shut her mouth upon me."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.16","order":"02.20.069.37639"},["b","16"],"Hear me, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; for thy lovingkindness",["i","is"],"good: turn unto me according to the multitude of thy tender",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"mercies"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.17","order":"02.20.069.37640"},["b","17"],"And hide not thy face from thy servant; for I am in trouble: hear me speedily."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.18","order":"02.20.069.37641"},["b","18"],"Draw",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"nigh"],"unto my soul,",["i","and"],"redeem it: deliver me because of mine enemies."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.19","order":"02.20.069.37642"},["b","19"],"Thou hast known my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"reproach"],", and my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"shame"],", and my dishonour: mine adversaries",["i","are"],"all before thee."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.20","order":"02.20.069.37643"},["b","20"],"Reproach hath broken my heart; and I am full of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"heaviness"],": and I looked",["i","for some"],"to take pity, but",["i","there was"],"none; and for comforters, but I found none."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.21","order":"02.20.069.37644"},["b","21"],"They gave me also gall for my meat; and in my thirst they gave me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"vinegar"],"to drink."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.22","order":"02.20.069.37645"},["b","22"],"Let their table become a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"snare"],"before them: and",["i","that which should have been"],"for",["i","their"],"welfare,",["i","let it become"],"a trap."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.23","order":"02.20.069.37646"},["b","23"],"Let their eyes be darkened, that they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"see not"],"; and make their loins continually to shake."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.24","order":"02.20.069.37647"},["b","24"],"Pour out thine indignation upon them, and let thy wrathful anger take hold of them."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.25","order":"02.20.069.37648"},["b","25"],"Let their habitation be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"desolate"],";",["i","and"],"let none dwell in their tents."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.26","order":"02.20.069.37649"},["b","26"],"For they persecute",["i","him"],"whom thou hast smitten; and they talk to the grief of those whom thou hast wounded."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.27","order":"02.20.069.37650"},["b","27"],"Add",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"iniquity"],"unto their iniquity: and let them not come into thy righteousness."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.28","order":"02.20.069.37651"},["b","28"],"Let them be blotted out of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"book"],"of the living, and not be written with the righteous."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.29","order":"02.20.069.37652"},["b","29"],"But I",["i","am"],"poor and sorrowful: let thy salvation, O God, set me up on high."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.30","order":"02.20.069.37653"},["b","30"],"I will praise the name of God with a song, and will magnify him with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.31","order":"02.20.069.37654"},["b","31"],["i","This"],"also shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"please"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"better than an ox",["i","or"],"bullock that hath horns and hoofs."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.32","order":"02.20.069.37655"},["b","32"],"The humble shall see",["i","this, and"],"be glad: and your heart shall live that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"seek"],"God."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.33","order":"02.20.069.37656"},["b","33"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"heareth the poor, and despiseth not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"his prisoners"],"."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.34","order":"02.20.069.37657"},["b","34"],"Let the heaven and earth praise him, the seas, and every thing that moveth therein."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.35","order":"02.20.069.37658"},["b","35"],"For God will save",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"Zion"],", and will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_35b"},"build"],"the cities of Judah: that they may dwell there, and have it in possession."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.36","order":"02.20.069.37659"},["b","36"],"The seed also of his servants shall inherit it: and they that love his name shall dwell therein."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.2a","order":"02.20.069.37660"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/130.1"},"Ps. 130:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.7.7-8"},"D&C 122:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.4a","order":"02.20.069.37662"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hate"},"TG Hate"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.5a","order":"02.20.069.37664"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/foolishness"},"TG Foolishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.9a","order":"02.20.069.37666"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/2.17.14-17"},"John 2:17 (14–17)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.9b","order":"02.20.069.37668"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproach"},"TG Reproach"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.10a","order":"02.20.069.37670"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.12a","order":"02.20.069.37672"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/30.9"},"Job 30:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.15a","order":"02.20.069.37674"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/16.33.31-33"},"Num. 16:33 (31–33)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.16a","order":"02.20.069.37676"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-mercy-of"},"TG God, Mercy of"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.18a","order":"02.20.069.37678"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/4.8.7-8"},"James 4:8 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.63"},"D&C 88:63"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.19a","order":"02.20.069.37680"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproach"},"TG Reproach"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.19b","order":"02.20.069.37682"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.20a","order":"02.20.069.37684"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/14.33.32-41"},"Mark 14:33 (32–41)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/despair"},"TG Despair"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.21a","order":"02.20.069.37686"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.34"},"Matt. 27:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/15.36"},"Mark 15:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/23.36"},"Luke 23:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/19.29.28-29"},"John 19:29 (28–29)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.22a","order":"02.20.069.37688"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.14.13-15"},"Isa. 8:14 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.9.9-12"},"Rom. 11:9 (9–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/18.14.13-15"},"2 Ne. 18:14 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.26"},"D&C 10:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.23a","order":"02.20.069.37690"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.25a","order":"02.20.069.37692"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/12.7"},"Jer. 12:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.5"},"22:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/23.38"},"Matt. 23:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.20.16-20"},"Acts 1:20 (16–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.27a","order":"02.20.069.37694"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/27.25.24-25"},"Matt. 27:25 (24–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.28a","order":"02.20.069.37696"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-life"},"TG Book of Life"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/record-keeping"},"Record Keeping"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.30a","order":"02.20.069.37698"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.38"},"Alma 34:38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/46.7"},"D&C 46:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.31a","order":"02.20.069.37700"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/15.22"},"1 Sam. 15:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.32a","order":"02.20.069.37702"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.38"},"D&C 101:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.33a","order":"02.20.069.37704"},["b","33a"],["span.small","OR"],"those that are in bonds for His sake."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.35a","order":"02.20.069.37706"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.9"},"Isa. 65:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"35b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/69.35b","order":"02.20.069.37708"},["b","35b"],["span.small","OR"],"rebuild."]]}
